    <item>
      <title>韩国誓言采取严厉行动恢复市场秩序，结束不当行为</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/korea-vows-tough-actions-to-restore-market-order-end-misconduct</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国政府监管机构在最近的行业调查中发出措辞强硬的警告，以恢复投资者信心，称如果在韩国经营的银行和其他金融公司收取过高的利率或逃避其他责任，将面临“严厉措施”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/korea-vows-tough-actions-to-restore-market-order-end-misconduct</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 02:31:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔推动国债下跌，中国股市回升：市场休整</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/treasury-selloff-hits-asia-on-pared-rate-cut-bets-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，政策制定者可能会等到三月之后再降息，随后美国国债下跌，延续了周五的抛售。在官方发出支持信号后，中国股市出现波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/treasury-selloff-hits-asia-on-pared-rate-cut-bets-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 22:33:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
